Fix any of the following:
  The link has insufficient color contrast of 2.14:1 with the surrounding text. (Minimum contrast is 3:1, link text: #40a7e3, surrounding text: #666666)
  The link has no styling (such as underline) to distinguish it from the surrounding text

relatedNode.nodeLabel: — Berger (@BergerofLondon) May 22, 2014
